{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/k8s_prac_1/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p><em>해당 포스트는 교재 『쿠버네티스 교과서』를 활용하며,</em><br>\n<em>환경은 Kubernetes v1.28. Docker Desktop으로 진행합니다.</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"k8s-개념-간단-정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#k8s-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90-%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"k8s 개념 간단 정리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>k8s 개념 간단 정리</h2>\n<h3 id=\"k8s\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#k8s\" aria-label=\"k8s permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>k8s</h3>\n<p>컨테이너를 실행 및 관리(오케스트레이션)하는 플랫폼<br>\n애플리케이션 시작, 롤링 업데이트, 서비스 수준유지, 스케일링 등 기능 제공.</p>\n<h3 id=\"k8s의-핵심\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#k8s%EC%9D%98-%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC\" aria-label=\"k8s의 핵심 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>k8s의 핵심</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>API - 애플리케이션 정의</li>\n<li>클러스터 - 애플리케이션 실행</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"클러스터란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%81%B4%EB%9F%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%84%B0%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"클러스터란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>클러스터란?</h3>\n<p>컨테이너 런타임이 동작하는 여러 대의 서버(Node)로 구성된 하나의 논리적 단위.<br>\nk8s 클러스터에서는 각각의 노드를 신경 쓸 필요가 없다. 클러스터가 알아서 관리!</p>\n<h3 id=\"노드란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%85%B8%EB%93%9C%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"노드란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>노드란?</h3>\n<p>컨테이너 런타임을 실행하는 서버.<br>\n노드중 일부는 k8s API를 실행하고 나머지는 컨테이너 속에서 동작하는 애플리케이션을 실행한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"배포-과정\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC-%EA%B3%BC%EC%A0%95\" aria-label=\"배포 과정 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>배포 과정</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>명령행 도구 등으로 원격에서 k8s API를 통해 애플리케이션 관리</li>\n<li>YAML 파일로 애플리케이션의 구성을 기술</li>\n<li>YAML이 클러스터에 전달되면 애플리케이션 배포</li>\n<li>추후 상황에 따라 노드의 대체나 컨테이너 재시작, 스케일링 등을 추가로 실행</li>\n</ul>\n<p>따라서 모든 클러스터에서 동일하게 동작하는 자기수복형 애플리케이션 구동이 가능하다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"k8s-기타-지원-기능\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#k8s-%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80-%EC%A7%80%EC%9B%90-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5\" aria-label=\"k8s 기타 지원 기능 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>k8s 기타 지원 기능</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>분산 데이터베이스<br>\n애플리케이션 구성 정보, API 키, 패스워드등 저장 가능</li>\n<li>스토리지<br>\n컨테이너 외부에 데이터 저장 가능. 고가용성 확보. 노드의 디스크나 공유 스토리지에 저장</li>\n<li>트래픽 관리</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"실습-환경\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%A4%EC%8A%B5-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\" aria-label=\"실습 환경 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>실습 환경</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Kubernetes v1.28. Docker Desktop</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"powershell\"><pre class=\"language-powershell\"><code class=\"language-powershell\"><span class=\"token function\">PS</span> C:\\Users\\hdyang\\Desktop\\Project\\k8s-practice> kubectl get nodes\r\nNAME             STATUS   ROLES           AGE   VERSION\r\ndocker-desktop   Ready    control-plane   16h   v1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>28<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>2\r\n<span class=\"token function\">PS</span> C:\\Users\\hdyang\\Desktop\\Project\\k8s-practice>   </code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"source\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#source\" aria-label=\"source permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Source</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>『쿠버네티스 교과서』- 엘튼 스톤맨, 길벗<br>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/gilbutITbook/kiamol\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/gilbutITbook/kiamol</a></li>\n</ul>","id":"7984dd4d-5792-5a0b-ba9c-5cdf77e03542","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#k8s-%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90-%EA%B0%84%EB%8B%A8-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\">k8s 개념 간단 정리</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#k8s\">k8s</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#k8s%EC%9D%98-%ED%95%B5%EC%8B%AC\">k8s의 핵심</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%ED%81%B4%EB%9F%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%84%B0%EB%9E%80\">클러스터란?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%85%B8%EB%93%9C%EB%9E%80\">노드란?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%B0%B0%ED%8F%AC-%EA%B3%BC%EC%A0%95\">배포 과정</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#k8s-%EA%B8%B0%ED%83%80-%EC%A7%80%EC%9B%90-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5\">k8s 기타 지원 기능</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%8B%A4%EC%8A%B5-%ED%99%98%EA%B2%BD\">실습 환경</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#source\">Source</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"『쿠버네티스 교과서』실습 1장","summary":"엘튼 스톤맨의 『쿠버네티스 교과서』를 바탕으로 k8s 실습을 진행합니다.","date":"2024.01.11.","categories":["K8s","Docker","DevOps"],"thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/582542484766a1b4ac3c5f037914dd69/bc134/k8s.jpg","srcSet":"/static/582542484766a1b4ac3c5f037914dd69/2278c/k8s.jpg 320w,\n/static/582542484766a1b4ac3c5f037914dd69/0f1c0/k8s.jpg 640w,\n/static/582542484766a1b4ac3c5f037914dd69/bc134/k8s.jpg 1280w","sizes":"(min-width: 1280px) 1280px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/582542484766a1b4ac3c5f037914dd69/378b7/k8s.webp 320w,\n/static/582542484766a1b4ac3c5f037914dd69/3c3fb/k8s.webp 640w,\n/static/582542484766a1b4ac3c5f037914dd69/c2dd8/k8s.webp 1280w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 1280px) 1280px, 100vw"}]},"width":1280,"height":720}},"publicURL":"/static/582542484766a1b4ac3c5f037914dd69/k8s.jpg"}}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/k8s_prac_1/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}